title: Record of Ragnarök: The Legend of Lu Bü Fengxian
description: The "Record of Ragnarök" spin-off! The thirteenth battle between mankind and the gods, with mankind's annihilation at stake. This is a legendary tale of the three kingdoms and their martial arts, depicting the legend of the representative of mankind, Lu Bü Fengxian, who fought in the first battle of the tournament!
author: Umemura Shin'ya
